Linden\">Hal Linden</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #99FF99; color: black; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" class=\"yes table-yes2\">Won\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Award_for_Best_Performance_by_a_Featured_Actor_in_a_Musical\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tony Award for Best Performance by a Featured Actor in a Musical\">Best Performance by a Featured Actor in a Musical</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Keene_Curtis\" title=\"Keene Curtis\">Keene Curtis</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #99FF99; color: black; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" class=\"yes table-yes2\">Won\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Award_for_Best_Direction_of_a_Musical\" title=\"Tony Award for Best Direction of a Musical\">Best Direction of a Musical</a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Michael_Kidd\" title=\"Michael Kidd\">Michael Kidd</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #FDD; color: black; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" class=\"no table-no2\">Nominated\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Award_for_Best_Choreography\" title=\"Tony Award for Best Choreography\">Best Choreography</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #FDD; color: black; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" class=\"no table-no2\">Nominated\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Award\" title=\"Tony Award\">Best Lyrics</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Sheldon_Harnick\" title=\"Sheldon Harnick\">Sheldon Harnick</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #FDD; color: black; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" class=\"no table-no2\">Nominated\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Award_for_Best_Scenic_Design\" title=\"Tony Award for Best Scenic Design\">Best Scenic Design</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/John_Bury_(theatre_designer)\" title=\"John Bury (theatre designer)\">John Bury</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #FDD; color: black; vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" class=\"no table-no2\">Nominated\n</td></tr><